<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>배달 주문 - 호텔 로봇 서비스</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* 공통 스타일 */
        body {
            background-image: url('/images/forest.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        .overlay {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }

        .header-title {
            color: white;
            font-size: 3rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .back-button {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            color: #a8d5aa;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* 음식 주문 페이지 전용 스타일 */
        .order-container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .main-content {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .order-sidebar {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            height: fit-content;
            position: sticky;
            top: 2rem;
        }

        .category-tabs {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            overflow-x: auto;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .category-tab {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            margin-right: 1rem;
            border: none;
            background: none;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #666;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .category-tab:hover {
            color: #2c5530;
            background: rgba(44, 85, 48, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        .category-tab.active {
            color: #2c5530;
            border-bottom-color: #2c5530;
            background: rgba(44, 85, 48, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        .menu-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .menu-item {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
        }

        .menu-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .menu-item-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f8f9fa, #e9ecef);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #2c5530;
        }

        .menu-item-name {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c5530;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .menu-item-description {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .menu-item-price {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c5530;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .add-to-cart {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #2c5530, #4a7c59);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .add-to-cart:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4a7c59, #2c5530);
            transform: scale(1.02);
            color: white;
        }

        .order-summary {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .order-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f8f9fa;
        }

        .order-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .item-info h6 {
            color: #2c5530;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .item-info small {
            color: #666;
        }

        .quantity-controls {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .quantity-btn {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 1px solid #2c5530;
            background: white;
            color: #2c5530;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .quantity-btn:hover {
            background: #2c5530;
            color: white;
        }

        .order-total {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c5530;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .customer-info {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .form-label {
            color: #2c5530;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .form-control {
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: #2c5530;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(44, 85, 48, 0.25);
        }

        .place-order {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #2c5530, #4a7c59);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .place-order:hover:not(:disabled) {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4a7c59, #2c5530);
            transform: scale(1.02);
            color: white;
        }

        .place-order:disabled {
            background: #6c757d;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            transform: none;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .order-container {
                padding: 0 15px;
            }

            .header-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .menu-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .category-tabs {
                padding-bottom: 10px;
            }
        }

    .menu-item-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: 150px; /* 네모 칸 높이 */
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        background-color: #f5f5f5; /* 이미지 없을 때 배경색 */
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        }

    .menu-item-image img.menu-image {
        max-width: 70%  ; /* 카드 안에서 적당히 작게 */
        object-fit: contain; /* 이미지 비율 유지 */
    }

    .img-80 {
        width: 80%;
    }
    .img-60 {
        width: 60%;
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="overlay">
    <div class="order-container">
        <a href="/" class="back-button">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> 메인으로 돌아가기
        </a>

        <h1 class="text-center header-title">
            <i class="fas fa-utensils me-3"></i>음식 주문
        </h1>

        <div class="row">
            <!-- 메인 메뉴 영역 -->
            <div class="col-lg-8">
